metadata.title: Chica Project Peer Leaders December 2024
topics: Life in Boston - what it is today, and what they hope it can be.

questions.question_text: What brought you or your family to Boston, and what has your experience been like?
When was a time you felt really supported by your community in Boston?
What do you worry about day to day while living in Boston?
Imagine a Boston 10 years from now that is fully inclusive to you and people like you. What does it look like?
What are you hearing during this conversation?
